{"title":"hexo个人博客搭建","uid":"059268b56602cb55de9c68eb7a3eddc3","slug":"hexo个人博客搭建","date":"2023-10-20T09:26:03.000Z","updated":"2023-10-20T09:34:42.733Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo个人博客搭建.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h3 id=\"hexo个人博客搭建\"><a href=\"#hexo个人博客搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo个人博客搭建\"></a>hexo个人博客搭建</h3><p>​\t前提需要安装node，建议用nvm安装</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>设置淘宝镜像（或者开vpn)</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">set</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">registry</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">https://registry.npmmirror.com/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>安装hexo</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo-cli</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>创建一个博客目录，并初始化，如果没有设置淘宝镜像或者vpn，这一步可能会失败，最好不要使用sudo初始化，要不然后续每次操作需要sudo提权很繁琐</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">mkdir</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">Blog</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">Blog</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">init</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>启动，此时可以访问了，如果想要终止ctrl+c</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">s</span></span></code></pre></div></li>\n<li><p>创建博客，可以用typora写markdown文件，然后放进source&#x2F;_posts目录下</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>配置主题：（<a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/en/guide/getting-started.html%EF%BC%89\">https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/en/guide/getting-started.html）</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>部署到github上，不建议使用gitee，需要手持身份证之类的比较麻烦</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#在github上创建一个仓库，项目名： 你的github用户名.github.io</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#安装插件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">hexo-deployer-git</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">--save</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#本地配置文件修改</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">vim</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">_config.yml</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#修改内容如下</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">deploy:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">  </span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">type</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">: </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">git</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">repo:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">https://github.com/tomarsqiu/tomarsqiu.github.io.git</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BABED8\">  </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">branch:</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">master</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#推送命令</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">hexo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">d</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#需要token登录，如果没有，创建一个，在github的setting </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#-&gt;developer setting </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#-&gt;personal access token</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#-&gt;tokens(classic)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#-&gt;generate new token</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#note里面是用来提示你这token用来做什么，可以自己随便填，下面的选项记得全部钩上，要不然到时候登录不了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#此时产生一个token，记得复制保存，以后见不到了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">输入你的用户名和token进行推送</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><p>输入https:&#x2F;&#x2F;你的github用户名.github.io&#x2F;进行访问，访问前记得进github刷新一下（如果你推送了的话）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>绑定域名，阿里云或者腾讯云购买一个域名，注册，备案</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","text":"hexo个人博客搭建​ 前提需要安装node，建议用nvm安装 设置淘宝镜像（或者开vpn) shellnpm config set registry http...","permalink":"/post/hexo个人博客搭建","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#hexo%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">hexo个人博客搭建</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"tomarsqiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/tomarsqiu","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"nvm安装","uid":"53ac39e10789bec03d342be6b8491c75","slug":"nvm安装","date":"2023-10-20T08:42:11.000Z","updated":"2023-10-20T08:48:16.190Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/nvm安装.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"nvm安装​ nvm是node的版本管理工具，可以安装多个版本的node并切换，直接从官网安装node，进行npm install时经常出错（需要sudo），所...","permalink":"/post/nvm安装","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":979,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"tomarsqiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/tomarsqiu","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}